"You can report bugs and feature requests at <ulink url=\"https://bugs.kde."
"org/enter_bug.cgi?product=NeoChat&amp;component=General\">https://bugs.kde."
"org/enter_bug.cgi?product=NeoChat&amp;component=General</ulink>"
msgstr ""
"Puoi segnalare bug e richiedere funzionalità su <ulink url=\"https://bugs."
"kde.org/enter_bug.cgi?product=NeoChat&amp;component=General\">https://bugs."
"kde.org/enter_bug.cgi? product=NeoChat&amp;component=General</ulink>"

